{
  "title": "Warm Crisp Syrian Pinto Bean Pilaf",
  "description": "A flavorful and healthy Syrian dish featuring pinto beans, ferment-jang, and a crisp texture, perfect for a lazy Sunday, this low-calorie-friendly pilaf is a great option for a relaxing meal.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
  "diet": [
